{
  "texts": [
    "Invariant Generation with ChatGPTOur goal is to provide initial insights into the capabilities of large language models, specifically ChatGPT, to support formal software verification.",
    "For this, we propose the task of loop invariant generation.",
    "Loop invariant generation.",
    "The goal of loop invariant generation is to generate valid and useful loop invariants for a given program.",
    "A valid loop invariant is an invariant that (1) holds true before the first loop execution and (2) after each loop iteration."
  ]
}